### 商品分类管理接口
### 服务: mall-product (端口 7200)
### 通过网关: http://localhost:1000/api/product/category/*

### ========== 1. 分类树查询 ==========

### 查询完整三级分类树
GET http://localhost:1000/api/product/category/tree

### ========== 2. 新增分类 ==========

### 新增一级分类
POST http://localhost:1000/api/product/category
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "图书、音像、电子书刊",
    "parentCid": 0,
    "sort": 1,
    "icon": "https://example.com/book.png",
    "productUnit": "件"
}

### 新增二级分类（parentCid 替换为实际的一级分类 ID）
POST http://localhost:1000/api/product/category
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "电子书刊",
    "parentCid": 1,
    "sort": 1,
    "productUnit": "本"
}

### 新增三级分类
POST http://localhost:1000/api/product/category
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "电子书",
    "parentCid": 2,
    "sort": 1
}

### 参数校验失败 - 名称为空
POST http://localhost:1000/api/product/category
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "",
    "parentCid": 0
}

### ========== 3. 修改分类 ==========

### 修改分类名称和排序
PUT http://localhost:1000/api/product/category
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "catId": 1,
    "name": "图书音像",
    "sort": 2
}

### 只修改图标
PUT http://localhost:1000/api/product/category
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "catId": 1,
    "icon": "https://example.com/new-icon.png"
}

### ========== 4. 拖拽排序 ==========

### 将分类从一个父节点拖到另一个父节点
PUT http://localhost:1000/api/product/category/sort
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "categories": [
        {
            "catId": 5,
            "parentCid": 2,
            "catLevel": 2,
            "sort": 1
        },
        {
            "catId": 6,
            "parentCid": 2,
            "catLevel": 2,
            "sort": 2
        }
    ]
}

### ========== 5. 批量删除 ==========

### 删除三级分类（无引用，应成功）
POST http://localhost:1000/api/product/category/batch-delete
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "ids": [3]
}

### 删除一级分类（应被拒绝）
POST http://localhost:1000/api/product/category/batch-delete
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "ids": [1]
}

### ========== 6. Actuator ==========

### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:7200/actuator/health
